'''Computo'''是一个[[拉丁语|拉丁语]][[词汇|词汇]]<ref name="Johnson1822">{{cite book|author=Samuel Johnson|title=A dictionary of the English language. Abstracted from the folio ed., by the author. To which is prefixed, A grammar of the English language. [Another]|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xJEUAAAAQAAJ&pg=RA6-PA7|year=1822|pages=6–}}</ref>，在[[古代|古代]][[法律|法律]]（archaic law）系统中，computo是一种[[令状|令状]]（writ）<ref name="English2000">{{cite book|author=Arthur English|title=A Dictionary of Words and Phrases Used in Ancient and Modern Law|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KVWH3SS7GBkC&pg=PA116|year=2000|publisher=Beard Books|isbn=978-1-58798-066-4|pages=116–|access-date=2020-07-24|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728144935/https://books.google.com/books?id=KVWH3SS7GBkC&pg=PA116|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其[[效力|效力]]可以[[强迫|强迫]]一个人交出[[账目|账目]]<ref name="Ogilvie1863">{{cite book|author=John Ogilvie|title=The Imperial Dictionary: English, Technological, and Scientific|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=O5hGAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA395|year=1863|publisher=Blackie and Son|pages=395–|access-date=2020-07-24|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812051925/https://books.google.com/books?id=O5hGAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA395|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是针对下列人员制定和执行的：
*[[第二遗嘱执行人|第二遗嘱执行人]]（executors of executors）；
*[[继承人|继承人]]的[[监护|监护]]人，对继承人在未成年时（未到法定年龄段）所做的或所遭受的重大破损等浪费进行赔偿；
*[[法警|法警]]；
*[[内侍|内侍]]；
*接受者<ref name="Roberts1847">{{cite book|author=Samuel Roberts|title=Digest of Select British Statutes, Comprising Those Which, According to the Report of the Judges of the Supreme Court Made to the Legislature, Appear to be in Force in Pennsylvania: With Some Others. With Notes and Illustrations|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=A7QwAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA9|year=1847|publisher=J. Kay, jun. & brother|pages=9–}}</ref>。

